text.plain: Uncomfortable health class subject, for short
Drink of choice for Captain Jack Sparrow
Martial art that uses bamboo swords
Rather warm, as a firelit room
Achieved, as a victory ... or how you might describe 17-, 25-, 47 and 55-Across
Female name that's a body part spelled backward
Strategically taps the ball into the infield
Poet whose first two initials stand for "Thomas" and "Stearns"
IDs written on applications, for short
Lab assistant often depicted with a hunched back
Name on a mailbox at the North Pole
Go down the slopes with a chute
One end to a boxing match, for short
Pushes down, as with the thumb
Coke and Pepsi, but not Sprite
One of three in an ellipsis
